2.0.0-beta1.name: drupal/insert_media

security-coverage.message: Beta releases are not covered by Drupal security advisories.

2.0.0-beta1.description: Assists in inserting media supplied by the Media Library widget into the body field as well as other editor and text areas. Please be aware that this module might not be part of the final Insert 2.0 release!
